    <p>It is important for your future success in the Creative Industries that you graduate with a functional knowledge of business and a solid set of business related skills. Your business specialization, consisting of a six-course module taught by the Ted Rogers School of Management and select core Creative Industries courses, is designed to address this goal.</p> 
<p>For details of the courses and tables below, see the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/calendar/2019-2020/programs/fcad/creative_industries/">course calendar.&nbsp;</a></p> 
