<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="562de472-042e-486b-b63a-5b2e8ad7022b" >

    <h2>Electives</h2> 
<p>These elective courses, required of all Ryerson students, are intended to broaden your education beyond your specific program of study. You will take one elective each term in your first three years. Typically students choose from a wide variety of courses offered in such areas as English, Philosophy, History, Political Science, Psychology, Musicology, Sociology and Economics.</p> 
<p>For details of the courses and tables below, see the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/calendar/2019-2020/programs/fcad/creative_industries/">course calendar.&nbsp;</a></p> 
<h2>Creative Industries Electives (Table I)</h2> 
<p>A minimum of 2 courses are to be selected from the following list in years 3 and/or 4:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/410.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/410/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 410</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/410.html">Beggars, Choosers: C.I. Advocacy</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/420.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/420/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 420</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/420.html">From Writer to Reader</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/430.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/430/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 430</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/430.html">Canadian Media and Entertainment Industries</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/450.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/450/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 450</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/450.html">Appreciating Creativity in Practice</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/500.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/500/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 500</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/500.html">Project Management</a></li> 
