 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/540.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/540/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 540</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/540.html">Marketing the Creative Industries</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/550.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/550/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 550</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/550.html">The Book in Canada</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/560.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/560/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 560</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/560.html">Topics in Creative Industries</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/570.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/570/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 570</a>: <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/570/">Creative Industries: International Lab</a></li> 
