 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/630.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/630/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 630</a>: <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/630.html">Advertising Theory and Practice</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/670.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/670/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 670</a>: <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/670/">Music and Brands</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/680.html" class="qTipCourse" data-url="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/creative-industries/CRI/680/jcr:content/center/uiwcalendarcourse.json">CRI 680</a>: <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/calendar/2019-2020/courses/creative-industries/CRI/680/">Celebrity</a></li> 
